EN: This grove of poplar trees turns golden in autumn, creating a beautiful scenery.

ZH: 杨树的树干是笔直的，具有很高的生长潜力。
EN: Poplar tree trunks are straight and have high growth potential.

ZH: 我喜欢在杨树下读书，那里非常宁静。
EN: I enjoy reading under a poplar tree, as it is very peaceful there.
